            <h1 id="ui-resourcegroups">Ressourcengruppen</h1>

            <h2 id="rg-connections">Verbindungen/Netze</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><b>Name:</b> Connections</li>
				<li><b>Identifier:</b> de.unistuttgart.ipvs.pmp.resourcegroups.connections</li>
				<li><b>Privacy Settings:</b>
					<table>
